rComments: Siobhan O'Flynn was my professor for a first years seminar called Digital Media and she made the course super enjoyable and easy to sit through a 3-hour lecture. The course was assignment based and even then they were not difficult. She is a very fair marker and is very approachable if you have any questions. Also replies to emails very quickly.

Very genuine, accessible, and hands on. Goes beyond the classroom to engage students with material and current events and issues. Understanding and flexible, yet she maintains a high degree of organization, expectations, and tact. Prof O'Flynn has many great resources and contacts and is very open to sharing them with her students.
One of the best- makes lectures very interesting by using a variety of tools to engage material. Very helpful as well

I loved being in Professor O'Flynn's class. She is passionate about both her area of study and her students. She was approachable and very helpful. I would love to take a course with her in the future.
She's passionate about her content and even organized a guest lecturer to come in at the end of the semester.  Very approachable.
